He's responsible for security operations in our company.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":12,"finishTime":14.8,"dialogue":{"text":"He's been with us for some time, nearly ten years.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":14.8,"finishTime":16.6,"dialogue":{"text":"He's tall and has curly hair.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":16.6,"finishTime":19.7,"dialogue":{"text":"He always has this vigilant look, probably a result of his job.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":20.3,"finishTime":22.2,"dialogue":{"text":"He sounds like a dedicated professional.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":22.2,"finishTime":25.5,"dialogue":{"text":"I've always wondered what the folks in security do around here.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":25.5,"finishTime":26.9,"dialogue":{"text":"What are his responsibilities?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":27.6,"finishTime":31.2,"dialogue":{"text":"He makes sure the company's data and facilities are secure,","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":31.2,"finishTime":35,"dialogue":{"text":"monitors access controls, and conducts investigations when needed.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":35,"finishTime":37.7,"dialogue":{"text":"He also ensures that everyone follows security procedures.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":38.2,"finishTime":41.8,"dialogue":{"text":"Ah, speaking of procedures, is there anything he's told you","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":41.8,"finishTime":44.6,"dialogue":{"text":"that we need to do when it comes to office security?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":45.1,"finishTime":47.3,"dialogue":{"text":"Yes, there is one thing he emphasizes:","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":47.3,"finishTime":50.9,"dialogue":{"text":"you mustn't share your access codes or passwords with anyone.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":50.9,"finishTime":52.6,"dialogue":{"text":"Security is a big deal for him.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":53.1,"finishTime":54.8,"dialogue":{"text":"Understandable. Well, thanks.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":55.4,"finishTime":57.6,"dialogue":{"text":"No problem. If you ever need any security tips,","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":57.6,"finishTime":59.2,"dialogue":{"text":"you really must talk to Jeff.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":{"x":125,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":59.7,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":{"x":-25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":60.1,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Dialog 3: Razgovor o Jeffu","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-discuss-roles-and-responsibilities","dashedName":"dialogue-3-talking-about-jeff","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disab